{
  "stem": "10478.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on, of course, when the occupation came, they showed to be also Nazi-friendly, yeah.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nazism was, according to myself, and according to the teachings in our church, was anti-Christian.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, in, in-- our church had a declaration announcing it, that anybody who became a member of the Nazi party was-- had to be dismissed and couldn't longer be a  member of the church.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That did actually happen, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, most of them, they resigned beforehand, because, you know, this-- that's what happens, usually.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that many, not that many.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was a small, little [? bit, ?] yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not at all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There wasn't-- no, there was  not even a problem, yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jews who lived in Holland were very-- still felt at home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I still remember that if there was an lottery for the-- for the Jewish cause, that our prime minister would-- on the-- on-- by radio, of course, ask the people to buy this for, for, for that-- for that cause, buy the lottery tickets.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I still remember our queen, Queen Wilhelmina at the time, had a special seat in the synagogue in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for occasions, she attended the synagogues.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She really was well [? in there. ?]",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the majority didn't know whether you were or not, because we went along with each other just like anybody else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the Germans, here, asked people to have an star on their-- on, on their jacket, or whatever-- then all of a sudden, hey, is that guy Jewish?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so, so, so, so [? it happened. ?] There was no problem there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not much.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, we hardly talked to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our neighborhood--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--never did any Jew live there at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- after the invasion, of course, they, well, had to print stuff that was handed over to them, by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before, they were-- had no-- everybody was comfortable with the, the Jews in Holland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had no problem with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Forced to, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took the editors away, and put the Nazi editors instead of that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they make this an-- a propaganda tool.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as result, we all-- we kind of cancelled the subscription to the papers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, never.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was, at that time, an, an a patient in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we, more or less, expected he was going to do something like that, even if Holland were neutral.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a surprise, of course, on May the 10th, all of a sudden, we was-- woke up in the morning, and there were hundreds of planes in the air.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had-- and, well, it was a shock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in the hospital, at that time, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a kidney ailment, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family was living in Maastricht, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All lived in-- at their home-- at their  home in Maastricht, yeah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not right away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not right away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- we were, at first, scared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then later on, they-- everything went back to normal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we, more or less, believed that there was nothing going on right away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That came on later, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the streets were, of course, filled with German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wherever you went, you know, there was soldiers walking around in uniform.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, some pro-Nazi Dutch people went on the street in their uniform.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had their own thing, set up their own party, the NSB.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and they had, had the same greetings as the Germans did, the Nazis did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not much except, of course, that, that we had to use food stamps for food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was-- less and less food we got, and bread, and meat, and butter, and that kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--rations yeah, right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, later on, they had a curfew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were not allowed to go on the street at-- after 8 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, until early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- there was plenty of work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- lots and lots of boys, aged 18 and 19 were taken away and brought to Germany for-- to work for the army.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- and there were quite a few.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then, of course, the, the empty places had  to filled with unemployed people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that way there was full employment going  on, yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lots of new laws came into effect, in a way, yeah, set up by Seyss-Inquart, who was the, the man who governed Holland on behalf of Hitler.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Seyss-Inquart.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, you ask me to do this?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Austria.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was an Austrian, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was a law of gatherings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not allowed to have big gatherings anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
